The area of SA is calculated on the condition of the required power pneed as shown in Eq. (2) (Colozza, 2003; Wang et al., 2009a; 2009b). The required power is determined by the power of all payloads ptotal, the output efficiency of the discharging unit ηdischarge, the efficiency of the electrolyzer ηelectrolyzer, the output efficiency of the fuel cell ηFC, and the duration of the night tnight. 2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
