				\begin{document}$${R_{\rm{u}}}(t) = {e^{ - \sum\limits_{i = {1}}^r {{\lambda _i}t}}},$$\end{document} where λi is the failure rate of the component i, r is the quantity of components in one RFC module, and t is the life time of the airship.

